app.use(helmet()); // sets X-Frame-Options, CSP, HSTS, X-Content-Type-Options, etc.
```

---

### 🟠 4. No Rate Limiting — OWASP A04 / DoS

There is no rate limiting on any endpoint. An attacker can hammer `/users` (or any future route) indefinitely — for enumeration, DoS, or credential stuffing if a login route is added later.

**Fix — add `express-rate-limit`:**
```js
