  console.error(err); // log internally — never send to client
  res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal server error' });
});
```

---

### 🔵 9. Hardcoded Data (Future Injection Risk)

User data is currently hardcoded, but when a database is added it will likely be passed directly into queries. Flag this now:

**When a DB is added, use parameterized queries or an ORM — never string interpolation:**
